Text: Northwest Power Pool System Schedulers Meeting Announcement October Cc meeting announcement FNdoc for the System Schedulers Meeting which will be held in Portland Oregon on October at The Benson Hotel Please note that the room reservation cutoff date is September th Also attached is the Meeting Attendance Confirmation Form Registrationdoc Please fax or email this form by October This year we are sending out a Burning Issues form Burning Issuesdoc for you to fill out and email to myself or drop in the box at the handouts table on the first meeting day We are hoping this will give everyone a chance to get their issues out on the table for discussion We look forward to seeing you at the meeting ChaRee Messerli Northwest Power Pool Ph Fax
